folder: Grand Street & Rodney Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
401-417 Grand Street, north side, east from Rodney Street. At left, first small house in 1870, was occupied by Mahler Bakery, and the fourth small house, Hagenbacker's clothing store.

November 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same; from the opposite direction.

November 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
